short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Shows all requested reviews in a GitHub repository.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Shows all requested reviews in a GitHub repository and assigned reviewers right in the currently open pull request or when creating a new pull request.


Data policy: The extension doesn't collect or share your data. GitHub tokens are only needed when you want to access private repositories or exceed GitHub API rate limit. The extension stores tokens in your browser storage and only uses them to authenticate with GitHub.
